{"tid":369144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖慎入！)覺唔覺香港啲公廁世界級嘔心","createTime":"2017-08-22T05:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T18:03:31.000Z","uid":17743,"like":49,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d002ef98252d8714a96ff541a3c6e68b41998e","tid":369144,"uid":17743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"香港啲公廁不論餐廳，狗鐵，公園廁所，商場，只要唔係高收入或者新嘅廁所，都污糟到廁所，係想嘔個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同強國差唔多其實，自問去過嘅國家地方唔多，但係日本，英國，德國etc。。佢地嘅廁所雖然有啲都係好核特，但係大部分都起碼乾淨，究竟係香港人自己用得衰定人地清潔做得足啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/133823_18fe03aaa6e27996f0926e3a6d60638c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F133823_18fe03aaa6e27996f0926e3a6d60638c.jpg&h=71cd4223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/133824_18fe03aaa6e27996f0926e3a6d60638c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F133824_18fe03aaa6e27996f0926e3a6d60638c.jpg&h=8438bb87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"016cb8a3173e0e36f1464e428c39f7c73a237c64","tid":369144,"uid":21102,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"廢老唔識自律 個括約肌又鬆 咪搞成咁"},{"pid":"16641fd3598fd9b0faed8fa370c0ed9c481330b1","tid":369144,"uid":9708,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"公廁應該搵人監場 見到有人搞污穢個廁格即刻發告票同捉去上屎坑培訓班"},{"pid":"a014338fbd2e8efb30187e25131844f78bdc67d9","tid":369144,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老唔識自律 <span style=\"color: red;\">個括約肌又鬆</span> 咪搞成咁</blockquote><br />\n公廁最多hehe <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764396fa4f27bc02198459431acd5e606191e5